Hungry? Want some noodles?

583
00:28:05,410 --> 00:28:07,560
No. I ate a lot at the company dinner.

584
00:28:07,560 --> 00:28:09,310
Mom, are you hungry?
How about some noodles?

585
00:28:10,250 --> 00:28:11,550
It's just a company dinner.

586
00:28:11,730 --> 00:28:12,570
Why are you so happy?

587
00:28:12,930 --> 00:28:14,110
Am I? I don't think so.

588
00:28:14,760 --> 00:28:16,110
Mom, have some plums.

589
00:28:16,930 --> 00:28:17,930
Where did they come from?

590
00:28:17,930 --> 00:28:18,770
It's a gift.

591
00:28:22,860 --> 00:28:24,360
♪You said♪

592
00:28:24,370 --> 00:28:27,610
♪I've got your back from now on♪

593
00:28:27,990 --> 00:28:32,800
♪Fried skewers, tofu skin,
and ice cream♪

594
00:28:34,740 --> 00:28:39,260
