595
00:28:40,410 --> 00:28:41,250
(Jiang)
Got home.

596
00:28:41,690 --> 00:28:43,180
Rest early.

597
00:28:43,520 --> 00:28:44,360
Good night.

598
00:28:44,820 --> 00:28:46,920
(Tang Yang)

599
00:28:46,930 --> 00:28:47,770
Not resting yet?

600
00:28:48,040 --> 00:28:49,100
Are you reading?

601
00:28:49,540 --> 00:28:54,060
(Jiang Shiyan)

602
00:28:54,760 --> 00:28:57,910
♪Like twin stars in perfect harmony♪

603
00:28:57,910 --> 00:28:59,370
♪Our meeting♪

604
00:28:59,370 --> 00:29:00,700
♪Is a great miracle♪

605
00:29:00,700 --> 00:29:04,110
♪We're meant to be together♪

606
00:29:04,110 --> 00:29:05,950
♪Inseparable♪

607
00:29:07,820 --> 00:29:12,820
(WeChat; Just now:
1 unread message from Tang Yang)

608
00:29:13,100 --> 00:29:16,980
(Tang Yang)

609
00:29:16,980 --> 00:29:19,510
♪Waiting for your reply♪

610
00:29:19,850 --> 00:29:21,200
♪Under the streetlamp's silhouette♪

611
00:29:21,200 --> 00:29:22,630
♪The mark of your lips still lingers♪

612
00:29:22,700 --> 00:29:25,430
♪Sweet words echo in my ears♪

613
00:29:27,970 --> 00:29:30,720
♪The melody♪

614
00:29:31,870 --> 00:29:34,370
♪The melody♪

615
00:29:43,520 --> 00:29:44,360
Not bad, right?

616
00:29:45,410 --> 00:29:46,250
Let me tell you.

617
00:29:47,010 --> 00:29:48,700
The noodles you made are amazing.

618
00:29:50,210 --> 00:29:51,070
You know this house.

619
00:29:51,280 --> 00:29:52,460
She's lived here for so long.

620
00:29:52,730 --> 00:29:53,630
But she hasn't moved.

621
00:29:54,250 --> 00:29:55,280
Didn't you say last time

622
00:29:55,280 --> 00:29:56,260
you wanted to get her

623
00:29:56,520 --> 00:29:58,180
a bigger place with an elevator?

624
00:29:58,450 --> 00:29:59,420
- Yes.
- She refused.

625
00:29:59,560 --> 00:30:01,280
Good thing the neighbor next door

626
00:30:01,280 --> 00:30:02,460
is selling their house,

627
00:30:02,730 --> 00:30:03,700
so you could buy it.

628
00:30:04,450 --> 00:30:06,040
Otherwise, what if the investors

629
00:30:06,040 --> 00:30:06,930
decide to investigate

630
00:30:06,930 --> 00:30:08,500
how many properties Mr. Jiang owns?

631
00:30:09,170 --> 00:30:10,010
They'll find out

632
00:30:10,650 --> 00:30:11,690
you and your mom live

633
00:30:11,690 --> 00:30:13,280
in a 66-square-meter old place.

634
00:30:13,280 --> 00:30:15,660
People would think
our company is a scam.

635
00:30:17,120 --> 00:30:18,110
As for this house,

636
00:30:19,250 --> 00:30:20,420
I persuaded him for 6 months.

637
00:30:21,410 --> 00:30:22,290
His daughter-in-law

638
00:30:22,290 --> 00:30:23,130
got pregnant later,

639
00:30:23,840 --> 00:30:24,760
so I told him to sell

640
00:30:24,760 --> 00:30:25,690
both his and his son's

641
00:30:25,690 --> 00:30:26,590
wedding house

642
00:30:27,250 --> 00:30:28,150
to buy a bigger one.

643
00:30:28,360 --> 00:30:29,200
That would be great.

644
00:30:30,250 --> 00:30:31,090
And it's all because

645
00:30:32,010 --> 00:30:33,790
of his grandson that he sold it to me.

646
00:30:34,040 --> 00:30:35,110
I paid an extra 200,000.

647
00:30:36,320 --> 00:30:37,700
You spent an extra 200,000?

648
00:30:38,760 --> 00:30:39,980
Are you crazy?

649
00:30:40,170 --> 00:30:41,250
This house is old.

650
00:30:41,250 --> 00:30:42,150
Won't hold its value.

651
00:30:42,280 --> 00:30:43,550
There's no room for appreciation.

652
00:30:44,420 --> 00:30:46,630
If Aunt really likes this area,

653
00:30:46,840 --> 00:30:47,840
you can just find her

654
00:30:47,840 --> 00:30:49,170
a nicer place nearby,

655
00:30:49,170 --> 00:30:50,420
and she can move over, right?

656
00:30:52,450 --> 00:30:53,900
She said it was left by my dad.

657
00:30:54,970 --> 00:30:55,810
If she moves,

658
00:30:56,280 --> 00:30:57,150
she'll sell it.

659
00:30:57,760 --> 00:30:58,600
She can't do that.

660
00:31:00,970 --> 00:31:01,830
So what should you do?

661
00:31:02,800 --> 00:31:03,940
You're still single.

662
00:31:04,250 --> 00:31:05,630
You don't have the qualifications.

663
00:31:06,040 --> 00:31:06,940
The house I have

664
00:31:07,560 --> 00:31:08,500
is under my mom's name,

665
00:31:09,210 --> 00:31:10,110
so I have a quota.

666
00:31:10,280 --> 00:31:12,150
What are you waiting for?
You should buy one.

667
00:31:12,970 --> 00:31:14,180
Why should I buy a house now?

668
00:31:16,760 --> 00:31:17,980
Are you nuts, Jiang Shiyan?

669
00:31:18,410 --> 00:31:19,930
New houses are quite cheap right now.

670
00:31:19,930 --> 00:31:20,770
What a good deal.

671
00:31:21,010 --> 00:31:22,660
I'm even planning to sell our old place

672
00:31:22,970 --> 00:31:24,630
in Rongcheng Duhui

673
00:31:24,800 --> 00:31:25,790
and buy a new one.

674
00:31:26,360 --> 00:31:27,800
These years, you didn't even take

675
00:31:27,800 --> 00:31:28,660
your dividends.

676
00:31:29,410 --> 00:31:30,840
Now, cash flow

677
00:31:30,840 --> 00:31:32,170
and profits are good.

678
00:31:32,170 --> 00:31:33,660
The Series C funding is coming.

679
00:31:33,970 --> 00:31:35,870
You can buy a pretty decent house.

680
00:31:37,800 --> 00:31:38,640
I'm planning

681
00:31:39,410 --> 00:31:40,870
to keep this quota for my

682
00:31:41,600 --> 00:31:42,440
future wedding house.

683
00:31:43,520 --> 00:31:44,360
Wedding house?

684
00:31:45,490 --> 00:31:46,330
Who's it for?

685
00:31:46,410 --> 00:31:47,250
Where is this person?

686
00:31:47,360 --> 00:31:49,030
You're not even at that stage.

687
00:31:49,280 --> 00:31:50,840
Your main goal right now

688
00:31:50,840 --> 00:31:52,010
should be to increase

689
00:31:52,010 --> 00:31:52,940
your fixed assets.

690
00:31:54,250 --> 00:31:55,090
No way.

691
00:31:55,490 --> 00:31:57,220
What if she has a house she likes

692
00:31:57,450 --> 00:31:58,290
but I can't buy it?

693
00:31:58,600 --> 00:32:00,180
But what if she has a quota?

694
00:32:01,920 --> 00:32:02,820
What if she's capable

695
00:32:02,840 --> 00:32:03,900
and she's bought a house?

696
00:32:04,250 --> 00:32:05,090
Well...

697
00:32:06,520 --> 00:32:07,660
You can always sell it.

698
00:32:09,010 --> 00:32:10,170
Enough, you're so annoying.

699
00:32:10,170 --> 00:32:11,010
Seriously.

700
00:32:11,600 --> 00:32:12,900
I'll just keep this quota

701
00:32:13,120 --> 00:32:14,310
and pick a house for her.

702
00:32:14,600 --> 00:32:15,940
It's that simple.

703
00:32:18,320 --> 00:32:19,250
It sounds like

704
00:32:19,250 --> 00:32:20,160
there's actually

705
00:32:20,160 --> 00:32:21,460
someone in your mind.

706
00:32:22,760 --> 00:32:23,790
Jiang Shiyan.

707
00:32:24,890 --> 00:32:26,490
We're back. Come help out.

708
00:32:26,490 --> 00:32:27,420
Tang is here too.

709
00:32:27,890 --> 00:32:28,730
Aunt.

710
00:32:30,210 --> 00:32:31,600
Aunt Yi, should I put this inside?

711
00:32:31,600 --> 00:32:33,320
Put it here, put it here.

712
00:32:33,320 --> 00:32:34,250
Let me help you.

713
00:32:34,250 --> 00:32:35,660
- No need.
- Lots of things to dry.

714
00:32:36,800 --> 00:32:37,940
What brings you here, Yang?

715
00:32:38,890 --> 00:32:40,010
I just happened to...

716
00:32:40,010 --> 00:32:41,320
- Feng is here too.
- Aunt.

717
00:32:41,320 --> 00:32:43,250
I came to find Jiang about something,

718
00:32:43,250 --> 00:32:44,210
and he mentioned someone

719
00:32:44,210 --> 00:32:45,790
was coming to fix the washing machine.

720
00:32:45,930 --> 00:32:47,050
I thought I'd hold a meeting

721
00:32:47,050 --> 00:32:48,070
at home with him.

722
00:32:48,890 --> 00:32:49,730
What brings you here?

723
00:32:50,360 --> 00:32:51,200
I...

724
00:32:51,520 --> 00:32:52,650
Her dad's friend,

725
00:32:52,650 --> 00:32:54,360
who used to do engineering,
visited them,

726
00:32:54,360 --> 00:32:55,590
with a lot of gifts.

727
00:32:55,730 --> 00:32:57,350
Ms. Zhou insisted I take some.

728
00:32:57,490 --> 00:32:58,460
How can I carry that all?

729
00:32:58,800 --> 00:32:59,760
Tang helped me.

730
00:32:59,760 --> 00:33:00,790
Just a little favor.

731
00:33:01,120 --> 00:33:01,960
Thank you.

732
00:33:02,450 --> 00:33:03,290
Thank you, Yang.

733
00:33:03,890 --> 00:33:05,110
Tang, are you hungry?

734
00:33:05,690 --> 00:33:06,630
Anything to eat at home?

735
00:33:06,890 --> 00:33:09,350
Jiang Shiyan just made some noodles
with savory sauce.

736
00:33:11,120 --> 00:33:12,660
Do you want it tossed or in soup?

737
00:33:12,840 --> 00:33:13,680
Mom, how about you?

738
00:33:13,840 --> 00:33:14,680
I'm not eating.

739
00:33:14,730 --> 00:33:15,730
I've been cutting back on

740
00:33:15,730 --> 00:33:16,660
my carb intake lately.

741
00:33:18,690 --> 00:33:20,110
I'll...

742
00:33:20,490 --> 00:33:21,980
Got it. I'll make one each,

743
00:33:22,320 --> 00:33:23,800
but use less noodles in each serving.

744
00:33:23,800 --> 00:33:24,690
If you can't finish,

745
00:33:24,690 --> 00:33:25,790
you can eat half each.

746
00:33:26,360 --> 00:33:27,200
Alright.

747
00:33:27,690 --> 00:33:28,530
Give me ten minutes.

748
00:33:29,320 --> 00:33:30,360
Okay, okay, let's go.

749
00:33:30,360 --> 00:33:31,450
Come on in, hurry.

750
00:33:31,450 --> 00:33:32,320
- Go inside.
- Aunt.

751
00:33:32,320 --> 00:33:33,490
- I'll carry your bag.
- OK.

752
00:33:33,490 --> 00:33:34,530
No need. Just go in.

753
00:33:34,530 --> 00:33:35,550
Let's go, let's go.

754
00:33:37,560 --> 00:33:38,400
Hurry up.

755
00:33:39,360 --> 00:33:40,200
Drink some water.

756
00:33:42,490 --> 00:33:43,700
Have you finished your meeting?

757
00:33:44,360 --> 00:33:45,550
We wrapped it up ages ago.

758
00:33:47,120 --> 00:33:47,960
Let me tell you.

759
00:33:48,560 --> 00:33:49,550
You know who's back?

760
00:33:49,730 --> 00:33:50,570
Who?

761
00:33:52,360 --> 00:33:53,200
Guess.

762
00:33:53,840 --> 00:33:54,790
I can't guess. Who?

763
00:33:55,410 --> 00:33:56,460
Chang Xinyi.

764
00:33:57,560 --> 00:33:58,400
She said

765
00:33:58,560 --> 00:34:00,080
she wants to gather with classmates

766
00:34:00,080 --> 00:34:00,970
next week.

767
00:34:00,970 --> 00:34:02,550
See if you're free
next Friday evening.

768
00:34:03,650 --> 00:34:04,760
Not many people will come.

769
00:34:04,760 --> 00:34:06,360
Maybe around ten.

770
00:34:06,360 --> 00:34:07,900
Anyway, whoever can will come.

771
00:34:10,120 --> 00:34:11,660
Chang Xinyi?

772
00:34:12,080 --> 00:34:12,920
Yeah.

773
00:34:13,120 --> 00:34:14,430
Jiang Shiyan's dream girl.

774
00:34:14,560 --> 00:34:16,070
His first love, you know.

775
00:34:18,810 --> 00:34:20,160
Even though they broke up,

776
00:34:20,160 --> 00:34:21,860
and I don't know why,

777
00:34:22,010 --> 00:34:22,910
but let me tell you.

778
00:34:23,640 --> 00:34:24,520
All these years,

779
00:34:24,520 --> 00:34:26,010
Jiang Shiyan hasn't dated anyone.

780
00:34:26,010 --> 00:34:27,240
It's definitely because

781
00:34:27,240 --> 00:34:28,470
he can't forget Chang Xinyi.

782
00:34:28,770 --> 00:34:30,680
Or, to put it another way,

783
00:34:30,680 --> 00:34:32,290
he hasn't found

784
00:34:32,290 --> 00:34:33,770
someone who can

785
00:34:33,770 --> 00:34:34,610
replace her.

786
00:34:38,010 --> 00:34:40,030
Isn't that a bit exaggerated?

787
00:34:40,970 --> 00:34:42,150
Am I exaggerating?

788
00:34:42,290 --> 00:34:44,380
Weren't you also...

789
00:34:53,680 --> 00:34:55,040
Weren't you also with Song Jing?

790
00:34:55,040 --> 00:34:55,880
You two.

791
00:34:56,290 --> 00:34:57,180
You don't even know.

792
00:34:57,640 --> 00:34:58,640
After you broke up

793
00:34:58,640 --> 00:34:59,630
with Song Jing,

794
00:34:59,810 --> 00:35:01,640
Jiang Shiyan told us not to mention him

795
00:35:01,640 --> 00:35:02,910
in front of you,

796
00:35:03,120 --> 00:35:04,030
lest it upset you.

797
00:35:05,240 --> 00:35:06,080
No.

798
00:35:06,330 --> 00:35:08,120
Song Jing and I...

799
00:35:08,120 --> 00:35:09,680
A first love. I get that.

800
00:35:09,680 --> 00:35:10,990
The meaning is different.

801
00:35:12,080 --> 00:35:12,930
- No.
- Just like

802
00:35:12,930 --> 00:35:13,910
Yanan and I.

803
00:35:14,330 --> 00:35:15,230
We're also first love.

804
00:35:15,240 --> 00:35:16,970
Thank goodness we ended up together.

805
00:35:16,970 --> 00:35:18,370
I can't even imagine

806
00:35:18,370 --> 00:35:19,660
how my life would be

807
00:35:20,240 --> 00:35:21,550
if I weren't with her.

808
00:35:23,890 --> 00:35:25,700
- He...
- Feng, why did you close the door?

809
00:35:29,290 --> 00:35:30,660
Why's the door closed?

810
00:35:31,200 --> 00:35:32,470
What are you hiding from me?

811
00:35:32,640 --> 00:35:33,510
You closed the door.

812
00:35:34,200 --> 00:35:36,590
What could I possibly be hiding?

813
00:35:37,120 --> 00:35:38,070
Have the soup first.

814
00:35:38,240 --> 00:35:39,680
I'll make you the tossed one later.

815
00:35:39,680 --> 00:35:40,740
- OK.
- Or it'll be mushy.

816
00:35:41,970 --> 00:35:42,820
Buddy,

817
00:35:42,930 --> 00:35:44,160
the toppings

818
00:35:44,160 --> 00:35:45,370
are more than mine.

819
00:35:45,370 --> 00:35:46,300
Give me another serving.

820
00:35:48,450 --> 00:35:49,740
Time to pick up your son, right?

821
00:35:51,200 --> 00:35:52,040
Oh, man.

822
00:35:52,120 --> 00:35:53,220
The noodles confused me.

823
00:35:53,330 --> 00:35:54,680
Well, I'm heading out now.

824
00:35:54,680 --> 00:35:55,780
Enjoy your meal.

825
00:35:56,040 --> 00:35:56,880
Aunt.

826
00:35:57,160 --> 00:35:58,080
I'm leaving

827
00:35:58,080 --> 00:35:59,030
to pick up my son.

828
00:35:59,410 --> 00:36:00,250
Okay.

829
00:36:00,520 --> 00:36:01,360
Is it hot?

830
00:36:01,850 --> 00:36:02,690
No.

831
00:36:04,080 --> 00:36:05,950
By the way, Feng Weiran just told me

832
00:36:06,200 --> 00:36:07,590
there's a class reunion next Friday.

833
00:36:07,770 --> 00:36:08,680
Not too many are going.

834
00:36:08,680 --> 00:36:10,380
Maybe about ten people.

835
00:36:11,290 --> 00:36:12,220
Are you going?

836
00:36:12,810 --> 00:36:13,650
Are you going?

837
00:36:14,370 --> 00:36:15,210
Well.

838
00:36:15,680 --> 00:36:17,860
It depends on if you're going.

839
00:36:19,370 --> 00:36:20,720
Doesn't this feel a bit

840
00:36:20,720 --> 00:36:21,660
childish?

841
00:36:22,490 --> 00:36:25,110
Also, I went to the last gathering.

842
00:36:25,410 --> 00:36:27,030
- So...
- I'll go then.

843
00:36:28,450 --> 00:36:29,430
I didn't go last time.

844
00:36:32,450 --> 00:36:33,430
So, are you going?

845
00:36:34,970 --> 00:36:35,930
I'll think about it.

846
00:36:35,930 --> 00:36:37,260
I might have to work overtime.

847
00:36:46,370 --> 00:36:47,470
Is the noodle not good?

848
00:36:48,450 --> 00:36:49,290
It's good.

849
00:36:49,290 --> 00:36:50,130
It's quite delicious.

850
00:36:50,770 --> 00:36:51,680
You don't look to be

851
00:36:51,680 --> 00:36:52,520
enjoying it to me.

852
00:36:53,560 --> 00:36:54,560
You used to slurp down

853
00:36:54,560 --> 00:36:55,430
a serving in no time.

854
00:36:55,970 --> 00:36:57,110
Now, you're eating so slowly.

855
00:37:05,080 --> 00:37:05,920
Don't burn yourself.

856
00:37:07,850 --> 00:37:08,720
I think I might have

857
00:37:08,720 --> 00:37:10,380
eaten something at my mom's place,

858
00:37:10,560 --> 00:37:11,470
so I'm not hungry now.

859
00:37:12,680 --> 00:37:13,520
I'll head back first.

860
00:37:13,680 --> 00:37:14,700
What about tossed noodles?

861
00:37:16,200 --> 00:37:17,340
No need. I'm full.

862
00:37:18,120 --> 00:37:19,220
Aunt Yi, I'm leaving.

863
00:37:19,770 --> 00:37:21,470
Tang, drive safely.

864
00:37:21,680 --> 00:37:22,520
Don't worry.

865
00:37:23,120 --> 00:37:24,180
See you. Bye-bye.

866
00:37:24,640 --> 00:37:25,480
Okay.

867
00:37:32,490 --> 00:37:34,300
I just checked.
There are about 15 items.

868
00:37:34,680 --> 00:37:36,010
Some of them are pretty good.

